keyFacts: A final pretrial conference for Ghislaine Maxwell was scheduled for November 1, 2021.
The conference was to be held in person at the Daniel Patrick Moynihan United States Courthouse (40 Foley Square) in New York.
The calendar entry was created on August 27, 2021, and modified on October 26, 2021, indicating ongoing case management.
The document is a logistical record from the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).
